{"tid":1632583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（圖）10月2號 當日全世界報紙頭版頭條","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:45:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T23:33:28.000Z","uid":324929,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"501d8330be3df72fe85882e6d3ac5be53ab95e80","tid":1632583,"uid":324929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:45:12.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人post過<br />\n令外想講一樣野<br />\n出面好多負面互屌post<br />\n希望大家冷靜d坐底討論下<br />\n<br />\n十月二號，全世界的紙媒報紙頭版頭條，香港！<br />\n<br />\n美國《The Wall Street Journal》<br />\n美國《The New York Times》<br />\n美國《The Washington Post》<br />\n英國《Financial Times》<br />\n英國《The Guardian》<br />\n英國《Independant》<br />\n意大利《La Repubblia》<br />\n意大利《il Giornale》<br />\n德國《Der Tagesspiegel》<br />\n西班牙《EL PAIS》<br />\n葡萄牙《Diario de Notcias》<br />\n<br />\n#HongKongers<br />\n#GaYao<br />\n#TheWholeWorldIsWatching<br />\n#WeConnectTheWorld<br />\n#StandingWithUS<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/023914_4bc5113f3ec5d9eabaedda999cffc3cd.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F07%2F023914_4bc5113f3ec5d9eabaedda999cffc3cd.jpeg&h=de78518d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oac7xuw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foac7xuw.jpg&h=fb30b7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUxZ72T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUxZ72T.jpg&h=cf7b85bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRGHmnV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRGHmnV.jpg&h=752fdedd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ow4ReHX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fow4ReHX.jpg&h=abca1a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/07/024009_f0ed87079e85efbe92ae40292004f244.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk